data.description: 20K PRICE DROP!  Charming 3-bedroom, 1.75 updated bath home in desirable Fircrest! Living room features a cozy wood burning fireplace. Spacious kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, island, and dining area with slider door to the fully fenced yard. Two bedrooms and bathrooms are located on the main floor, along with laundry. On the upper level you will love the large bedroom and storage space.   Partially finished basement and attached 1-car garage. Bring some TLC and make this your new home!  Conveniently close to Cheney Stadium, schools, parks, shopping, and much more!
